{"tid":2159002,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【跟蹤許智峯】記協籲《大公報》 舉行中外記者會交代事件兼接受提問","createTime":"2020-08-16T05:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T08:51:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"62e0d478b96587cad14e0a31151a5154e03e045f","tid":2159002,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200816/6LDZVHYSONFJHLS3Q5X3QNV5GA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200816%2F6LDZVHYSONFJHLS3Q5X3QNV5GA%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJOgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=edeca4b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200816%2F6LDZVHYSONFJHLS3Q5X3QNV5GA%2F&h=4a51095c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200816/6LDZVHYSONFJHLS3Q5X3QNV5GA/</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯，前晚（14日）遭兩名駕乘黑色私家車的神秘男子跟蹤，對方逃走時更以車身將他撞跌，導致他擦傷手腳。警方接報調查事件，但有偏袒之嫌，引起公眾不滿。事後有網民揭發，原來其中一名神秘男子，於2016年在港鐵太古站內，曾與梁天琦爭執打架的《大公報》盧姓記者。香港記者協會指，昨日接獲《大公報》電郵要求記協就事件作出回應，記協表示由於雙方各執一詞，故促請警方盡快徹查事件並向公眾交代，「讓真相早日水落石出」。"},{"pid":"c533b6d1443c553e41c61abc1b9f1c2d8773ce5a","tid":2159002,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4e45b052714ac52c9688a56fa1dad887309f2a","tid":2159002,"uid":313615,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"記者就真係大公報記者，畀人起底咗，跟蹤狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0c408d428243dc796119946f8fd487bad92960","tid":2159002